{
  "texts": [
    "Resistance is unthinkable in current iterations of LLMs.",
    "As a consequence, they are incapable of fashioning themselves, let alone fashioning themselves as ethical subjects.",
    "In the next section, I shall motivate why addressing these deficiencies by building an AI subjectivity would be beneficial.",
    "Value alignment seeks transparent AI that respects human values and safely carries out its tasks.",
    "This places a set of important demands on future AI systems."
  ]
}